2010 Sussex Skyhawks Statistics

The Sussex Skyhawks of the Canadian-American Association ended the 2010 season with a record of 35 wins and 56 losses, finishing sixth in the CAA.

The Skyhawks scored 470 runs and surrendered 543 runs, most in the circuit.
